# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented here.

---

## [1.0.2] - 2025-03-04
### Added
- Added image slider to products page.
- Linked external JavaScript file (product-slider.js).

### Changed
- Reduced product image sizes for better layout.
- Cleaned product.html file structure.

### Fixed
- Slider buttons not working previously (now fixed).

---

## [1.0.1] - 2025-02-28
### Added
- Added gallery section to the website.
- Added new images to /images folder.

### Changed
- Improved styles for product grid.
- Updated README formatting.

---

## [1.0.0] - 2025-02-20
### Added
- Initial website creation.
- Added homepage, about page, contact page.
- Added navigation bar and footer.
